<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-blue);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Landscaping &amp; External Works</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Surfacing &amp; Access</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Surfacing and access across London and the South East — car parks and hardstanding, roads, footpaths and cycleways, permeable paving and drainage, line marking and signage. The trafficked surfaces that take the load and manage the water, built to BS 7533 with SuDS detailed to the CIRIA manual and accessible routes to Part M.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Surfacing &amp; Access →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Surfacing &amp; Access,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Car parks &amp; hardstanding</li><li>Roads, footpaths &amp; cycleways</li><li>Permeable paving &amp; drainage</li><li>Line marking &amp; signage</li><li>Sub-bases &amp; formation</li><li>Falls, gullies &amp; SuDS features</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 7533 — paving &amp; block surfacing</li><li>CIRIA SuDS Manual (C753) — sustainable drainage</li><li>Building Regs Part M — accessible routes &amp; parking</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you handle external drainage, SuDS and permeable paving?</summary><p>Yes. We design and build surface-water drainage as part of the surfacing — including permeable paving and SuDS features detailed to the CIRIA SuDS Manual (C753) — so the surfacing and the drainage are delivered by one team.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you surface a car park around a live, occupied building?</summary><p>Yes. Much of our surfacing is phased around live sites — out-of-hours access, segregated routes and protected pedestrian flows under CDM 2015 — so parking and access stay open while we work section by section.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do car parks and footpaths meet accessibility requirements?</summary><p>Yes. Accessible bays, dropped kerbs, tactile paving and footpath gradients are set out to meet Building Regs Part M, with line marking and signage delivered as part of the same package.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Landscaping &amp; External Works</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; External Works overview</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/hard-landscaping/">Hard Landscaping</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/soft-landscaping/">Soft Landscaping</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/boundaries/">Boundaries &amp; Features</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Groundworks</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme and stage if you can.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Enquire about MEPH →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/compliance/">Compliance &amp; BSA</a></div></div></div></section></div><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{@site.url}}/"